div.pure-u-1.pure-u-sm-1-1.pure-u-md-2-5.pure-u-lg-3-10(data-scroll-reveal="ease-in after 0s")
    div.content

        div.carousel
            div: img.slide(data-lazy="assets/hunt-and-peck1.png")
            div: img.slide(data-lazy="assets/hunt-and-peck2.png")
            div: img.slide(data-lazy="assets/hunt-and-peck3.png")

        div.banner
            h1.project-title Hunt & Peck
            h2.project-subtitle Twister Meets Fighter
            a.button(href="static/hunt-and-peck/" target="_blank") Play
            a.button(href="https://bitbucket.org/RandomGuy928/experimentalgamejam1/" target="_blank") Source

        div.text
            :markdown
                Challenged with a theme of physical space, Hunt & Peck is an experimental mashup between Twister and Pro Wrestling (NES), featuring 8-bit fighting, and randomized controls. Offering a fun and goofy experience in which two may enter, and only one can leave ... Collectively programmed in Unity over a span of three days, with Alex Foo, [Arthur Jones](//arthurjonesportfolio.weebly.com/), and Dustin Tsui.